title: Railworks TS2014 AP Class 90 FL
description:
In assocation with Waggonz, Armstrong Powerhouse presents the class 90 in two brand new liveries as well as a brand new FWA wagon. Please check out the feature list below to see exactly what it has to offer :

Class 90 - 2 liveries (Freightliner & Freightliner Powerhaul)

FWA Wagon - 10 container liveries & 2 container variants (Standard & High Cube)

Detailed internal & external audio

Accurate performance physics

Prototypical braking system (rheostatic/air)

Random locomotive faults

Speed set (cruise control)

Cold start option

'Quick Drive' consists

And much, much more!

As well as the rolling stock, three authentic scenarios are included for the WCML Over Shap route.

Extra Stock and the Pack Branding Patch can be downloaded from the AP website.



Please support the developers and buy some of their content if you can afford it.


Please use the email address or the facebook fanpage for requests, questions and also if you want to share an addon with the community which we will post on your behalf.

If you would like to contribute, please read the Readme.pdf.




A Team tpb_4_ever upload.
